methodsArray.push( [ 'CostanzoRecipes_Desserts_StrawberryCake', '<p><ol><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Preheat oven to 325°F (170°C). </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Line two 8-inch round cake pans with parchment paper. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> In the top of a double boiler, combine eggs and sugar. Cook over simmering water, stirring occasionally, just until an instant-read thermometer registers 98°F (37°C). </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> In the bowl of a stand mixer fitted with the whisk attachment, beat the egg mixture at high speed for 4 minutes; reduce mixer to medium speed and beat until you can see clear ribbons in batter, about 5 minutes. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-3\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-3" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-3", 240)</script><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-3", 300)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> In <amount original_amount="a small" fraction="1.000000000000" units="small">a small</amount> microwave-safe bowl, heat milk on high heat for 30 seconds.<img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-4\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-4" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-4", 30)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Sift one-third of flour over egg mixture. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Using a rubber spatula gently fold until combined. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Repeat procedure with remaining flour in two additions. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Add warm milk and melted butter and gently fold until combined, stopping to scrape sides and bottom of bowl to ensure everything is incorporated. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Pour into prepared pans. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Lightly tap pans on counter a few times to release any big air bubbles. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> bake until a wooden pick inserted in center comes out clean, 18 to 25 minutes. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-5\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-5" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-5", 1080)</script><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-5", 1500)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Spray a wire rack with cooking spray. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Vigorouly tap pans once on counter. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Invert cakes onto prepared rack and let cool for 15 to 20 minutes <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-6\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-6" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-6", 900)</script><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-6", 1200)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Turn right side up and let cool completely. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> In the bowl of a stand mixer fitted with the whisk attachment beat all Whipped Cream ingredients at high speed until soft to stiff peaks form. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Level cooled cake layers, if necessary. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Place one cake layer on a cake plate. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Spread <amount original_amount="¾ cup" fraction="0.750000000000" units="cup">¾ cup</amount> Whipped Cream on first cake layer.</li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Slice all but 3 strawberries into ⅛-inch slices and arrange in a single layer over Whipped Cream atop the first cake layer. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Spread <amount original_amount="¼ cup" fraction="0.250000000000" units="cup">¼ cup</amount> more Whipped Cream over the strawberries.</li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Top with second cake layer. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-7\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-7" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-7", 0)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Spread remaining Whipped Cream on top and sides of cake, decorating as desired. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Top with remaining strawberries, sliced in half. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Refrigerate in an airtight container for up to 2 days. </li></ol>' ] );
