methodsArray.push( [ 'CostanzoRecipes_Bread_RusticSourdoughTwoWays', '<p><ol><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Combine all ingredients except for the fruit and nuts, kneading to form a smooth dough. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Allow the dough to rise in a covered bowl until doubled in size, about 90 minutes. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-1\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-1" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-1", 5400)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Gently divide the dough in half; it\'ll deflate somewhat. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Knead the fruit and nuts into half the dough. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Shape the dough into two rounds or oval loaves, as desired. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Place in flour brotforms or couche or towel-lined bowls. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Cover and let rise until very puffy, about 1 hour. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-2\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-2" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-2", 3600)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Toward the end of the rising time place a baking stone or steel in the oven and preheat to 425°. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Turn the risen loaves over onto <amount original_amount="a piece" fraction="1.000000000000" units="piece">a piece</amount> of parchment.</li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Spray the loaves with lukewarm water and dust generously with flour. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Make two fairly deep diagonal slices in each. Use firm, quick motions; a sharp knife or lame works well here. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Slide loaves onto the stone. </li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Bake the breads for 25 to 30 minutes, until they are a very deep golden brown. <img src="images/alarm-clock-icon.png" onclick="toggleElement(\'CircularTimer-3\')" class="alarm-clock-icon"><div id="CircularTimer-3" class="circular-timer-container"><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-3", 1500)</script><script>new CircularTimer("CircularTimer-3", 1800)</script></div></li><li onclick="handleItemClick(this)"> Remove from the oven and cool on a rack. </li></ol>' ] );
